  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frayspace is a fast-paced and physics-based space arena shooter with fully destructible maps. You have several fighter ships to choose from and a wide range of weapons at your disposal to destroy your enemies in arenas that have unique environmental hazards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/1d2f2fe3330763d76941d0d54d165245.poster.avif?t=1749202413\" width=584 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/1d2f2fe3330763d76941d0d54d165245.webm?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/1d2f2fe3330763d76941d0d54d165245.mp4?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced player-vs-player twin-stick battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer: split-screen for 4 and a shared screen Chaos mode for 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based fighter ship controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 40 fully destructible maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nine fighter ships with active shield mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bunch of weapons from spitfire to lasers, bombs, and seek'n'destroy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-ups like time control, shockwave, and the melter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game modes: deathmatch, last man standing, capture the flag and conquest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modifiable settings, such as damage, friendly fire, and respawn time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/a5e2b571aa8103e599f7e0842f3d36ab.poster.avif?t=1749202413\" width=584 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/a5e2b571aa8103e599f7e0842f3d36ab.webm?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/a5e2b571aa8103e599f7e0842f3d36ab.mp4?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mastering the fast-paced action requires skill</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose to challenge your friends to all-vs-all combat or fight in teams in multiple game modes – deathmatch, last man standing, capture the flag and conquest. The AI players offer quite a challenge too! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Split-screen and shared screen local multiplayer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All game modes are playable in split-screen with up to 4 players and enabling the Chaos mode allow up to 8 players to join the fight on a shared screen. Frayspace supports Steam Remote Play, so remote matches are an option too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/f762c270fa345cd84145a953579fc84d.poster.avif?t=1749202413\" width=292 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/f762c270fa345cd84145a953579fc84d.webm?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/f762c270fa345cd84145a953579fc84d.mp4?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/8cf5bf7367f95d604bf750ff64a8c8cc.poster.avif?t=1749202413\" width=292 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/8cf5bf7367f95d604bf750ff64a8c8cc.webm?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/8cf5bf7367f95d604bf750ff64a8c8cc.mp4?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanics</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each fighter ship has unique specs including health, shield, speed, and weapon damage. They are equipped with an active shield that can block enemy attacks with right timing - its effective use depends on using it at the right moment. The weapons inflict distinct damage to both health and shield of the fighters. Choose your weapon wisely, as the shield halves the damage inflicted to health. You can find many kinds of power-ups like time control, the shockwave and the nuke in the maps and use them to your advantage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/c616b5f8eae6b3fb18cad0f9094e5160.poster.avif?t=1749202413\" width=584 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/c616b5f8eae6b3fb18cad0f9094e5160.webm?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/c616b5f8eae6b3fb18cad0f9094e5160.mp4?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Music by Alexey Kasyanchuk (DEgITx) (CC license)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frayspace is a fast-paced and physics-based space arena shooter with fully destructible maps. You have several fighter ships to choose from and a wide range of weapons at your disposal to destroy your enemies in arenas that have unique environmental hazards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/1d2f2fe3330763d76941d0d54d165245.poster.avif?t=1749202413\" width=584 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/1d2f2fe3330763d76941d0d54d165245.webm?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973100/extras/1d2f2fe3330763d76941d0d54d165245.mp4?t=1749202413\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced player-vs-player twin-stick battles</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local multiplayer: split-screen for 4 and a shared screen Chaos mode for 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Physics-based fighter ship controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than 40 fully destructible maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nine fighter ships with active shield mechanics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bunch of weapons from spitfire to lasers, bombs, and seek'n'destroy</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-ups like time control, shockwave, and the melter</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game modes: deathmatch, last man standing, capture the flag and conquest</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Modifiable settings, such as damage, friendly fire, and respawn time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinl